[ COMBAT LAW ]

Enemy move power is not direct damage by itself.

Formula:
    damage = max(1, movePower + enemyAttack - playerDefense)

Exceptions:
    * Pocket Sand = 1 damage
    * Constrict = normal hit + 2 damage per trapped turn


